summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing a contract for the sale and conveyance of land and buildings of certain City Property (Lots 9, 10, 11 and 12, Block H of A.A. Denny's 4th Addition) in the Pike Place Urban Renewal Project (WASH. R-17) Disposition Parcels Nos. 6 and 7) to the Elliott Bay Partnership No. 1.
